                <div class="origin-story">
                    <p>The Third Voice was born in a deeply personal crisis — a breakdown in communication during a time of extreme emotional stress while I was detained. In those moments, I realized that most human conflict stems not from lack of care, but from misfired communication.</p>
                    
                    <p>I envisioned something new: a calm, emotionally intelligent "third voice" that could help people hear each other when emotions run high.</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>Not a chatbot. Not a therapist. But a digital co-mediator — present in the moment when it matters most.</strong></p>
